    <exercise id="fs-id1862083" type="conceptual-questions"><problem id="fs-id1423142">
    <para id="import-auto-id1354976">Define mechanical energy. What is the relationship of mechanical energy to nonconservative forces? What happens to mechanical energy if only conservative forces act? </para>
